   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can <xref href="DeActUserAcc.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Deactivate a User Account</xref> to prevent a user from accessing the application. On deactivating an account, the user cannot log into the application. However, the account is not deleted, and all details of the account are retained and available. </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can <xref href="ActUsrAcc.dita" class="- topic/xref ">Active a User Account</xref>.  On activating an account, the user can log in to resume working on the application.</p>
